- [crowd gasps]
- [girl] Oh, my God!

33:36.473 --> 33:38.684
[grunting]

33:41.770 --> 33:43.814
What're you doing?

33:43.897 --> 33:46.316
- [overlapping chatter]
- [Susannah] Stop it.

33:46.400 --> 33:48.318
Both of you, stop it.

33:55.993 --> 33:59.538
What is going on?

34:03.834 --> 34:04.835
Mom...

34:09.255 --> 34:10.299
We know, Mom.

34:11.759 --> 34:13.844
We both know.

34:13.927 --> 34:15.929
[♪ Phoebe Bridgers: "Funeral"]

34:18.264 --> 34:20.350
Know what?

34:23.978 --> 34:25.647
[sniffles]

34:25.731 --> 34:27.733
[crying]

34:32.070 --> 34:34.031
I feel so stupid.

34:35.407 --> 34:38.911
Honey, why would you
feel stupid?

34:38.994 --> 34:41.996
Because, all summer long,

34:42.080 --> 34:43.916
I've been thinking about myself,

34:43.998 --> 34:46.001
and Susannah was sick,
and I didn't even know.

34:46.083 --> 34:47.460
Okay.

34:47.543 --> 34:49.963
That's how she wanted it.

34:50.047 --> 34:52.966
It's exactly how she wanted it.

34:54.802 --> 34:56.469
How long have you known?

34:58.055 --> 35:00.516
Since the spring.

35:00.599 --> 35:03.894
She didn't want to
burden you kids with it.

35:03.977 --> 35:07.314
She wanted one last summer
with you guys.

35:10.025 --> 35:11.318
But what about you?

35:12.611 --> 35:14.154
What about me?

35:15.405 --> 35:17.825
You had to carry it
all by yourself.

35:17.908 --> 35:20.369
♪ And I have this dream
where I'm screaming ♪

35:20.452 --> 35:22.788
♪ Underwater ♪

35:22.871 --> 35:25.707
♪ While my friends
are all waving ♪

35:25.791 --> 35:29.127
♪ From the shore ♪

35:29.211 --> 35:32.381
♪ And I don't need you
to tell me ♪

35:32.464 --> 35:34.466
♪ What that means ♪

35:34.550 --> 35:35.926
[door opens]

35:36.009 --> 35:38.679
♪ I don't believe
in that stuff anymore...

35:38.762 --> 35:41.139
She's not gonna
get better, is she?

35:42.182 --> 35:43.642
No.

35:52.818 --> 35:55.112
♪ Jesus Christ ♪

35:55.195 --> 35:57.656
♪ I'm so blue all the time ♪

35:57.739 --> 36:01.869
♪ And that's just how I feel ♪

36:01.952 --> 36:04.538
♪ Always have ♪

36:04.621 --> 36:08.709
♪ And I always will ♪

36:08.792 --> 36:12.921
♪ I always have
and always will ♪

36:25.767 --> 36:28.353
[Susannah] I'm so sorry
the night turned out like this.

36:30.564 --> 36:33.066
It's not how I wanted you
to find out.

36:33.150 --> 36:36.111
Mom, you're gonna do
the trial, right?

36:39.615 --> 36:41.033
Uh...

36:41.116 --> 36:43.160
No, honey.

36:43.243 --> 36:44.369
I'm not.

36:44.453 --> 36:46.496
I can't.

36:48.123 --> 36:50.667
Chances are very slight.

36:50.751 --> 36:53.503
Uh, nonexistent, really, and...

36:54.880 --> 36:58.008
I just can't
go through that again.

36:58.091 --> 37:00.218
It was too hard the first time.

37:00.302 --> 37:02.471
[Jeremiah] Mom,
but you could try.

37:02.554 --> 37:05.140
You have to try.

37:05.223 --> 37:08.226
I just want to be me when I go.

37:09.603 --> 37:11.021
- Does that make sense?
- No.

37:11.104 --> 37:12.940
No, it doesn't make sense.
None of this makes any sense.

37:13.023 --> 37:15.275
I know, I know.

37:15.359 --> 37:17.903
I'm not good at this. Okay?

37:17.986 --> 37:20.864
Mommy's not good at this.

37:26.578 --> 37:28.121
I should've known that you knew.

37:31.249 --> 37:33.168
I just didn't want
to believe it.

37:34.670 --> 37:37.506
Mom, if there's any chance,
you have to.

37:37.589 --> 37:38.715
I mean, you have to.

37:38.799 --> 37:40.550
Come on, tell her, Conrad.

37:41.969 --> 37:44.680
Why aren't you saying anything?

37:44.763 --> 37:45.931
Mom, this is crazy.

37:46.014 --> 37:48.266
You have to try.
You can't give up on us.

37:48.350 --> 37:50.143
[Conrad] Mom?

37:50.227 --> 37:53.230
Can't you just...

37:53.313 --> 37:55.023
I mean, can't you just try?

37:56.733 --> 37:58.402
For us, Mom?

38:01.113 --> 38:02.489
I need you.

38:04.157 --> 38:05.784
Come here.

38:05.867 --> 38:09.413
♪ I'm so blue all the time ♪

38:09.496 --> 38:13.166
♪ And that's just how I feel ♪

38:13.250 --> 38:16.878
♪ Always have, and I always ♪

38:16.962 --> 38:19.339
♪ Will ♪♪

38:26.596 --> 38:29.182
[scoffs] Okay,
I know it's end times

38:29.266 --> 38:31.351
- if you're cooking.
- Shut up.

38:33.311 --> 38:35.564
How'd it go with the boys?

38:35.647 --> 38:36.982
[sighs]

38:37.065 --> 38:38.650
I told them I'd do the trial.

38:40.193 --> 38:42.279
I couldn't say no.

38:44.322 --> 38:47.451
I know it's gonna
make things harder, but...

38:47.534 --> 38:49.286
I don't care
what the doctors say.

38:49.369 --> 38:50.704
It's going to work.

38:52.456 --> 38:53.790
You're magic. [chuckles]

38:53.874 --> 38:55.876
[chuckles]

38:55.959 --> 38:57.919
[sniffles] Since when
do you believe in magic?

38:58.003 --> 39:01.298
[chuckles] I believe in you.

39:07.179 --> 39:10.015
All right, everybody down here.
We still have to eat.

39:10.098 --> 39:12.517
[overlapping chatter]

39:14.936 --> 39:17.022
- [Laurel] Thank you, no.
- Laurel!

39:17.105 --> 39:18.899
[Belly] There were times
this summer when I felt like

39:18.982 --> 39:20.108
I didn't know my own heart.

39:20.192 --> 39:21.276
You want some ice cream?

39:21.359 --> 39:22.652
[Belly] But one thing I do know

39:22.736 --> 39:24.738
for sure is that, no matter

39:24.821 --> 39:27.157
what happens next,
I will always come back

39:27.240 --> 39:29.201
to this place

39:29.284 --> 39:31.203
and these people.

39:31.286 --> 39:32.913
[chatter continues]

39:42.506 --> 39:44.800
I can't believe she said yes.

39:46.093 --> 39:48.512
You did it.
You changed her mind.

39:48.595 --> 39:50.972
Oh, it wasn't me.
It was Jere. He did it.

39:57.479 --> 39:59.940
Belly, I'm sorry
for being so shitty

40:00.023 --> 40:01.983
all summer.

40:04.653 --> 40:07.447
I mean, you were going
through all this alone.

40:07.531 --> 40:09.699
[stammers] I wish you had
told me so you didn't have to.

40:09.783 --> 40:11.952
I wanted to.

40:12.035 --> 40:14.162
I almost did a couple of times.

40:14.246 --> 40:16.289
- [♪ Taylor Swift: "This Love"]
- ♪ Tossing, turning ♪

40:16.373 --> 40:19.251
♪ Struggled through the night...

40:19.334 --> 40:22.087
Um, we should go in.

40:22.170 --> 40:24.256
There's so many things
I want to say to you.

40:24.339 --> 40:25.423
Don't. Not now.

40:25.507 --> 40:26.967
Why?

40:29.886 --> 40:31.304
'Cause you really,
really, really need

40:31.388 --> 40:33.098
somebody right now, and...

40:33.181 --> 40:34.474
I don't want to be
the kind of person

40:34.558 --> 40:35.600
who takes advantage of that.

40:35.684 --> 40:36.935
I don't just need somebody.

40:40.480 --> 40:41.690
I need you.

40:43.692 --> 40:46.111
I don't want you to need me.

40:46.194 --> 40:48.238
I want you to want me.

40:48.321 --> 40:51.158
♪ You showed up just in time...

40:51.241 --> 40:54.077
I do want you.

40:54.161 --> 40:57.414
♪ This love is good,
this love is bad ♪

40:57.497 --> 41:01.835
♪ This love is alive back
from the dead, oh, oh, oh ♪

41:01.918 --> 41:04.087
♪ These hands had to
let it go free ♪

41:04.171 --> 41:06.715
♪ And this love came back ♪

41:06.798 --> 41:08.425
♪ To me, oh, oh, oh ♪

41:08.508 --> 41:11.219
♪ Your kiss, my cheek ♪

41:11.303 --> 41:14.639
♪ I watched you leave ♪

41:14.723 --> 41:17.058
♪ When you're young,
you just run ♪

41:17.142 --> 41:20.061
♪ But you come back ♪

41:20.145 --> 41:22.814
♪ To what you need ♪

41:27.277 --> 41:30.655
♪ This love is good,
this love is bad ♪

41:30.739 --> 41:32.699
♪ This love is alive ♪

41:32.782 --> 41:34.201
♪ Back from the dead...

41:34.284 --> 41:36.703
[Belly] In this moment,
I realized

41:36.786 --> 41:41.124
if this can happen,
maybe anything can.

41:41.208 --> 41:44.044
♪ This love left
a permanent mark ♪

41:44.127 --> 41:48.173
♪ This love is glowing
in the dark, oh, oh, oh ♪

41:48.256 --> 41:50.675
♪ These hands had to
let it go free ♪

41:50.759 --> 41:54.429
♪ And this love came back to me,
oh, oh, oh ♪

41:54.512 --> 41:57.390
♪ This love, oh, oh, oh ♪

41:57.474 --> 41:58.892
♪ This love ♪

42:00.560 --> 42:02.395
♪ This love ♪

42:03.730 --> 42:08.735
♪ This love, this love
came back to me, oh, oh, oh ♪♪

42:09.986 --> 42:11.988
[waves crashing]

42:41.059 --> 42:43.061
[waves continue crashing]

43:12.132 --> 43:14.134
[waves continue crashing]
